Copies the navigation-menu family to your JTE root. Compose top-level items in the `content` slot:

  @template.lievit.navigation-menu(label = "Main", content = @`
    @template.lievit.navigation-menu.link(href = "/", label = "Home", activeHref = currentHref)
    @template.lievit.navigation-menu.menu(id = "products", label = "Products", content = @`
      @template.lievit.navigation-menu.link(href = "/products", label = "All products",
          description = "Browse the catalogue", icon = "package", inPanel = true)
    `)
  `)

Panels open via [popover=auto] (native Esc + click-outside close). Requires popover-anchor.enhancer.ts and collection-nav.enhancer.ts registered in your runtime.
